@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.79
    v2 = (0.61 + (v0 + (v1 + 0.29 / v2 + 0.08)))
    v1 = 0.30
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.38 * tmp + 0.23) - (v2 + 0.22 - tmp + 0.12)) / wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.06)))
    v0 = 0.28
    v2 = wp.cos((v2 + v1))
    v0 = v0
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v2 + 0.74 - tmp + 0.42)))
    data[tid] = v0
